snippet.title: Winter Survival – Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Check the demo here and add the game to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394960/Winter_Survival/

We're thrilled to announce that our brand-new demo for Winter Survival is available right now! Brave the elements, gather materials to craft a better equipment and hunt or be hunted. Early Access coming on February 28th, 2024!
